data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_ResourceItems_Property
data.value: Gets the resources collection.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_IsPolling_Property
data.value: Gets the value indicating whether the connector is currently polling for changes on the Exchange server.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_PollingInterval_Property
data.value: Returns or sets the interval at which the client will poll the server for changes. The default is 30 seconds.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_ServerConnectionSettings_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the settings used to connect with the Microsoft Exchange Server.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_UseDefaultCredentials_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether one of the users should be the user currently logged on to the system.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_Users_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the collection of users whose calendars should be retrieved from the server.

data.name: ExchangeScheduleDataConnector_UseServerWorkingHours_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether the custom working hours should be downloaded from the server for each user.

data.name: Resources_Customizer_Property
data.value: Returns the Infragistics.Shared.ResourceCustomizer for this assembly.

data.name: ExchangeUser_Domain_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the domain or computer to which the user belongs.

data.name: ExchangeUser_Password_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the password of the user.

data.name: ExchangeUser_UserName_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the user name of the user.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_AcceptGZipEncoding_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether the server should return information compressed with GZip.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_CookieContainer_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the cookies associated with the server.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_HttpHeaders_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the HTTP headers which should be sent with each request to the server.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_PreAuthenticate_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the value indicating whether HTTP pre-authentication should be used when connecting to the server.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_RequestedServerVersion_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the requested version of the server.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_Timeout_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the timeout used when requesting information from the server, in milliseconds.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_Url_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the URL to the Microsoft Exchange Server.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_UserAgent_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the value of the user-agent HTTP header.

data.name: ExchangeServerConnectionSettings_WebProxy_Property
data.value: Gets or sets the web proxy used when connecting to the server.
